        <text x="110" y="252" font-family="'Share Tech Mono',monospace" font-size="8" fill="#ccffcc">Intestinal epithelium replaced every 4–5 days via stem cells (Clevers, 2011)</text>
        <text x="110" y="270" font-family="'Share Tech Mono',monospace" font-size="8" fill="#ccffcc">Haematopoietic stem cells: ~200 billion blood cells/day. Without them — tissue failure (Poliwoda et al., 2022)</text>
